                  <dt>Exhibition History</dt>
          <dd>
                          <p>
                              <em>Twelfth Summer Exhibition</em>, New Gallery, London, 04/24/1899 - 08/07/1899
                            </p>
                          <p>
                              <em>Twenty-Ninth Autumn Exhibition of Modern Pictures in Oil and Water-Color</em>, Walker Art Gallery, Liverpool, Liverpool, 09/04/1899 - 01/06/1900
                            </p>
                          <p>
                              <em>Exhibition of the Collected Works of W. Holman Hunt, O.M., D.C.L.</em>, Leicester Galleries, London, 10/06/1906 - 11/17/1906
                            </p>
                          <p>
